The carillon has almost
played its whole tune.

1:17:56.976 --> 1:17:58.108
- Then the time has come.

1:17:59.413 --> 1:18:00.197
[dramatic music]
- Sophie!

1:18:05.593 --> 1:18:08.771
[music box tinkling]

1:18:11.687 --> 1:18:13.036
- What's wrong, Sophie?

1:18:14.864 --> 1:18:16.822
- Aunt Annabelle doesn't care.

1:18:25.788 --> 1:18:28.704
- Come on, you know
that's not true.

1:18:28.747 --> 1:18:30.749
Don't ever think that.

1:18:30.793 --> 1:18:33.621
[banging]

1:18:33.665 --> 1:18:38.844
[ominous rumbling]
[window shutters banging]

1:18:44.545 --> 1:18:48.158
