1:19:41.559 --> 1:19:43.474
[giggling]

1:19:43.517 --> 1:19:48.696
[eerie music]
[electricity buzzing]

1:19:51.961 --> 1:19:54.790
[Lania giggling]

1:19:59.142 --> 1:19:59.925
I'm here!

1:20:05.148 --> 1:20:05.975
Ha!

1:20:28.432 --> 1:20:31.522
[crickets chirping]

1:20:39.660 --> 1:20:43.142
[ominous music]

1:20:43.186 --> 1:20:46.406
[music box tinkling]

1:20:46.450 --> 1:20:49.496
[Sophie sobbing]

1:20:55.938 --> 1:20:56.764
- Sophie!

1:20:58.766 --> 1:21:01.160
- You didn't go away.

1:21:01.204 --> 1:21:04.033
- I will never go away, okay?

1:21:04.076 --> 1:21:06.209
I will never go away, okay?

1:21:07.253 --> 1:21:08.515
Now, let's go!

1:21:13.303 --> 1:21:18.482
[suspenseful music]
[music box tinkling]

1:21:48.816 --> 1:21:52.472
- [Mrs. Potter] I heard the
carillon play its entire melody.

1:21:52.516 --> 1:21:53.952
I had never heard the
whole thing through.

1:21:53.996 --> 1:21:55.823
It would always get stuck.

1:21:55.867 --> 1:21:57.216
- It didn't work

1:21:57.260 --> 1:22:01.133
because it didn't play
the whole melody yet.

1:22:01.177 --> 1:22:04.615
Sophie, you have
to listen to me,

1:22:04.658 --> 1:22:07.574
I have to bury the
carillon now, okay?

1:22:07.618 --> 1:22:09.141
You stay here.

1:22:09.185 --> 1:22:10.751
Don't leave this room, okay?

1:22:13.189 --> 1:22:15.104
- [Sophie] Don't go!

1:22:15.147 --> 1:22:16.975
- You have to trust me.

1:22:17.019 --> 1:22:18.846
Everything will be okay.

1:22:18.890 --> 1:22:21.284
Just stay here, okay, okay.

1:22:23.112 --> 1:22:23.895
Okay?

1:23:03.979 --> 1:23:06.938
[raspy humming]

1:23:12.378 --> 1:23:15.294
[ominous music]

1:23:18.732 --> 1:23:20.778
- [Sophie] Aunt Annabelle!

1:23:30.614 --> 1:23:33.443
[Sophie shrieks]

1:24:00.774 --> 1:24:03.429
[Sophie sobbing]

1:24:03.473 --> 1:24:06.128
[door slams]

1:24:10.915 --> 1:24:16.051
[music box tinkling]
[ominous music]

1:24:27.453 --> 1:24:32.763
[Annabelle sobbing]
[crickets chirping]

1:24:36.897 --> 1:24:37.985
- Sophie!

1:24:41.250 --> 1:24:42.077
Sophie!

1:24:45.428 --> 1:24:46.820
Sophie.

1:24:46.864 --> 1:24:49.214
